#compdef mdbook-toc
# Documentation: https://github.com/badboy/mdbook-toc
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-19
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# mdbook-toc is a preprocessor invoked by mdbook; it accepts only -h/--help
# and -V/--version, all configuration lives in book.toml under
# [preprocessor.toc].

_arguments -s -S \
  '(- *)'{-h,--help}'[show help]' \
  '(- *)'{-V,--version}'[show version]' && return 0
